description: Baronessa is off to enjoy some time in the forest, but unfortunately she is disturbed by a naughty guy in a wheelchair and his attendant. The attendant finds himself overpowered and bound to a bed where he will soon undergo a breathtaking adventure. The wheelchair bound man is unable to escape on his own and is made to watch every wicked sex act done to his attendant. But soon, he too will know that his handicap isn't enough to keep the sadistic Mistress away. She tosses him out of his wheelchair to use him as a dildo holder. Soon he finds himself in a SM studio. Bound with rubber and a rope around his neck, he is suspended out of his wheelchair. Baroness absolutely knows no mercy!
title: Handicapped
